ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend Swahili to another student. It is well-paced and the work load is very fair.

I would recommend Swahili to other students interested in learning the language. It is a course that focuses more on reading and writing than previous years, but introduces some new grammar later in the semester.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class will help me with a future career. I hope to work with refugees, and knowledge of Swahili will definitely help me in a new job.
By helping me learn the language, this course helped me establish area studies proficiency in Swahili-speaking areas.
